<p>  <!-- EDIT THIS: carnival introduction begins with this paragraph: -->
<p> Welcome to the April 21, 2009 edition of a speed cleaning carnival. </p>
<h2>Home</h2>
<p>  <!-- Carnival Submission -->
<p> <b>Gary R.</b> presents <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog/2009/04/15/basic-camping-first-aid/">Basic Camping First Aid</a> posted at <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog">Camping Tips</a>, saying, &#8220;Nothing ruins your camping trip like a brush with poison ivy, a pesky bee sting or other minor injury.&#8221; </p>
<p>  <!-- Carnival Submission -->
<p> <b>Gary R.</b> presents <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog/2009/04/04/working-at-a-campground/">Working at a Campground</a> posted at <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog">Camping Tips</a>, saying, &#8220;So, you say you love camping so much you wish you could do it year round? Well, why not take a job working at a campground?&#8221; </p>
<p>  <!-- Carnival Submission -->
<p> <b>Gary R.</b> presents <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog/2009/03/15/how-to-build-a-campfire/">How to Build a Campfire</a> posted at <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog">Camping Tips</a>, saying, &#8220;You don&#8217;t need a Boy Scout merit badge to build a roaring fire at your campsite - all you need are a few simple supplies and the following technique.&#8221; </p>
<p>  <!-- Carnival Submission -->
<p> <b>Gary R.</b> presents <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog/2009/03/11/easy-to-prepare-campsite-meals/">Easy to Prepare Campsite Meals</a> posted at <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog">Camping Tips</a>, saying, &#8220;When you&#8217;re packing up for your big camping trip, the last thing you want to do is to weigh down your car with all the extra pots, pans and kitchen utensils you&#8217;ll need to prepare your favorite meals over the camp stove.&#8221; </p>
<p>  <!-- Carnival Submission -->
<p> <b>Gary R.</b> presents <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog/2009/03/23/how-to-buy-hiking-boots/">How to Buy Hiking Boots</a> posted at <a href="http://campingearth.com/blog">Camping Tips</a>, saying, &#8220;Good quality hiking boots aren&#8217;t cheap, but trust me - the expense is well worth it! If you&#8217;re planning a major camping or hiking outing, the last thing you want is a pair of cheap boots that causes you injury or falls apart in the middle of your journey.&#8221; </p>
<p>  <!-- Carnival Submission -->
<p> <b>Tom Maurer</b> presents <a href="http://www.simpleandspiritual.com/simplify-the-bathroom/">Simplify The Bathroom</a> posted at <a href="http://www.simpleandspiritual.com">Simple and Spiritual</a>. </p>
<p>   <!-- EDIT THIS: the conclusion begins with this paragraph: -->
<p>That concludes this edition.  Submit your blog article to the next edition of <b>a speed cleaning carnival</b> using our <a target="_blank" title="Submit an entry to “a speed cleaning carnival”" href="http://blogcarnival.com/bc/submit_6909.html">carnival submission form</a>. Past posts and future hosts can be found on our <a target="_blank" title="Blog Carnival index for “a speed cleaning carnival”" href="http://blogcarnival.com/bc/cprof_6909.html"> blog carnival index page</a>.</p>
