      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal_68D387F9_011F_1000_ADD2_28F66ACAE16C_40000"><span lang="NL">How to get the grouts between your tiles clean again?</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal_68D387F9_011F_1000_ADD2_28F66ACAE16C_40000"><span lang="NL"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-32" title="grout" src="http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/grout.jpg" alt="grout" width="117" height="91" />You get a new bathroom or kitchen. It looks great and you wish it could stay like that forever. Unfortunately after some time your tiles do not look so good anymore. Dirt settles on the grouts and a normal all-purpose cleaner just does not do the trick no more. But do not worry, there are a lot of ways to clean the grouts to make your bathroom or kitchen shine again. Start by trying some natural products.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal_68D387F9_011F_1000_ADD2_28F66ACAE16C_40000"><span lang="NL">Take an old toothbrush and some diluted bleach, apply on the grouts, let it sit for some time. Then rinse with water. Be careful with your clothes when working with bleach and do not forget to ventilate the area you are working in. You can also try this with vinegar. You have to clean the grouts afterwards the usual way. Another natural product you can try is backing powder, mix with some water and apply, again with the toothbrush and rinse.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal_68D387F9_011F_1000_ADD2_28F66ACAE16C_40000"><span lang="NL">In case of a severe filthyness when the grouts are molded and nothing seems to work, buy a professional cleaner especially for this purpose. In that case it is probably a good idea to check the ventilation of your bathroom to prevent similar problems in the future. There are also products to paint the grouts, you can chose a colour close to the original if you want them to look like before. But if you chose a colour that contrasts strongly with your tiles, it can lead to an extraordinary result. Always follow the instructions closely not to damage the tiles. </span></p>
