      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>Too many posts to handle? If you missed out on a great post from last month, here&#8217;s a quick digest of the top posts that you may want to check out:</div>
<ul style='padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;margin-top:15px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px'>
<li style='padding-bottom:15px'><b><a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/general-overview-of-cleaning/cleaning-closets-how-can-you-organize-your-closet' style='color:#0000FF'>Cleaning closets. How can you organize your closet. </a></b>
<div><small>Posted on Friday, March 13th, 2009 in <a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/?cat=5'>General overview of Cleaning</a> - Comments: (0)</small></div>
<div>How can you organize your closet.Now that winter is almost over and spring will take over most people will want to clean out and reorganize their closet. What to do with your winter clothes which take up so much space. One idea is to buy special bags you can fill and then suck out the air with your vacuum. That way you can store them for instance in a suitcase or in the attic or under your bed.</div>
</li>
<li style='padding-bottom:15px'><b><a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/cleaning-floors/cleaning-hardwood-floors-how-to-maintain-and-clean-hardwood-floors' style='color:#0000FF'>Cleaning hardwood floors. How to maintain and clean hardwood floors.</a></b>
<div><small>Posted on Monday, March 23rd, 2009 in <a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/?cat=25'>Cleaning Floors</a> - Comments: (0)</small></div>
<div>How to maintain and clean hardwood floors.Hardwood floors are an asset to any house. They are not cheap in purchase but with proper care they can last a lifetime. Have you ever been to England and visited a stately home or castle? Changes are great they will have a hardwood floor that has been there for centuries with thousands of visitors  walking over them.</div>
</li>
<li style='padding-bottom:15px'><b><a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/general-overview-of-cleaning/general-overview-of-cleaning' style='color:#0000FF'>General overview of cleaning</a></b>
<div><small>Posted on Friday, March 20th, 2009 in <a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/?cat=5'>General overview of Cleaning</a> - Comments: (0)</small></div>
<div>General overview of cleaningIt is no astonishing that every people wanted their house to be arranged and organized. Even animals want the same thing for their quarters. However, for some of us, the job of house cleaning may not appear as simply as it may sound.The huge query that everyone ask about the job of house cleaning is; where do I start?</div>
</li>
<li style='padding-bottom:15px'><b><a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/clean-a-bathroom/how-to-clean-a-bathroom' style='color:#0000FF'>How to Clean A Bathroom</a></b>
<div><small>Posted on Thursday, March 12th, 2009 in <a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/?cat=4'>Clean a Bathroom</a> - Comments: (0)</small></div>
<div>How To clean Your BathroomThe bathroom is the room all members of the family use every day to wash themselves by taking a shower or bath. We also use it to put on make-up or brush our teeth. It can get messy in there and it is very important to keep it clean and hygenic. This is how to clean your bath or shower fast and thorough.</div>
</li>
<li style='padding-bottom:15px'><b><a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/clean-a-bathroom/how-to-clean-a-bathroom-step-by-step' style='color:#0000FF'>How to Clean a Bathroom Step-by-Step</a></b>
<div><small>Posted on Tuesday, March 17th, 2009 in <a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/?cat=4'>Clean a Bathroom</a> - Comments: (0)</small></div>
<div>How to Clean a Bathroom Step-by-StepThe cleanest part of the house should be the bathrooms however it is very terrible to get cleaned up. Sadly, it’s a bit filthy work to get done but you really have to do it. When doing the general house cleaning, it is best to collect all your cleaning supplies in a single bin where in you can take around from one area to another.</div>
</li>
<li style='padding-bottom:15px'><b><a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/carpet-care/how-to-remove-carpet-stains' style='color:#0000FF'>How to remove carpet stains?</a></b>
<div><small>Posted on Friday, March 13th, 2009 in <a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/?cat=10'>Carpet Care</a> - Comments: (1)</small></div>
<div>How to remove carpet stains?The most important factor in removing carpet stains out of your precious carpet or rug is to act immediately. Do not wait foir the stain to settle in or you will be too late. All that is left you then is a professional  carpet stain removal and it may even not work as good as you expect.</div>
</li>
<li style='padding-bottom:15px'><b><a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/carpet-care/mattress-care' style='color:#0000FF'>Mattress Care</a></b>
<div><small>Posted on Friday, March 13th, 2009 in <a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/?cat=10'>Carpet Care</a> - Comments: (0)</small></div>
<div>Do you know how to take care of your mattress?Sleeping is an important part of our daily routine, without it we will eventually not function properly any more. Besides that, we like spending time in bed, we spend about a third of our live in it. So we want our bed to be comfortable and look nice if possible. But believe it or not, our bed can also make some people ill or what you do not see is just as important.</div>
</li>
<li style='padding-bottom:15px'><b><a href='http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/speed-cleaning-tips-clutter-control/amazon-home-speed-cleaning-tips-clutter-control-organized-happy-home-100-guaranteed' style='color:#0000FF'>Now Available On Amazon!</a></b>
