      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>How to Clean a Bathroom Step-by-Step<br />
<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-38" title="clean-bathroom1" src="http://www.speedcleaninganswers.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/clean-bathroom1.jpg" alt="clean-bathroom1" width="124" height="104" />The cleanest part of the house should be the bathrooms however it is very terrible to get cleaned up. Sadly, it’s a bit filthy work to get done but you really have to do it. When doing the general house cleaning, it is best to collect all your cleaning supplies in a single bin where in you can take around from one area to another. At the same time, you would also need to have another bin that can clutch the bathroom cleaning supplies like the soap scum and mildew remover, bathroom surface cleaner, window washing fluid, toilet bowl cleaner, dust rags, paper towels, sponges scrub brush and floor cleaner.<br />
When having your bathroom cleaned, the very first thing to do is to take off any dirty clothes or dirty towels and make certain that everything is in the proper place. Take out all the rugs that need to get washed. Cleaning up the shower is the most difficult thing to get done when cleaning the bathroom. The shower is area where in the soap scum and mildew is building up when it is not regularly cleaned. Since having the shower cleaned might make use the most of your energy, it is best to have it cleaned first. When the soap scum in the shower is truly dreadful, you can let the cleaner to soak it up for a little while before you begin to scrub it. Also take time to clean up the shower curtain or shower door and of course the track. There are loads of different products that are specifically manufactured for cleaning the shower. It’s really up to you what kind of product you are going to make use of. Make sure to properly rinse off the shower with water after cleaning it as it would just clear off the other flowing dirt and substances.<br />
When you are done cleaning the shower, the next thing to have cleaned are the mirrors. People in the house usually like to write up messages to one another in the mirror after a warm shower have got it all smoggy. However, the disadvantages are it causes smudges on the mirror. So therefore make use of your rags to have it cleaned.<br />
The next thing which needs to get cleaned is the sink involving the facets. All products intended to clean up the bathroom or the kitchen surfaces will also do the same thing for the entire sink. When the cleaning of the sink is over, the next thing you have to get done is cleaning up the toilet which is obviously the filthiest part. The inner part of the toilet will get cleaned by using a regular toilet brush and a small amount of toilet bowl cleaner or a not reusable toilet bowl cleaner. The other parts of the toilet such as the rim of the bowl, the under part of the lid and the seat also need to get cleaned and wipe up. A good surface cleaner will work well in cleaning the back part of the toilet and the area where in some people overlook or the pedestal.<br />
And last but not the least, is mopping the floor of the bathroom and emptying the garbage cans. Using paper towels in cleaning the bathroom is a good practice although it is more eco-friendly to make use of sponges or rags. The good thing about using paper towels is, after you have utilized it to wiped off some areas of the bathroom, you can have it thrown in the garbage which means, you are also throwing away some germs that you have taken from the areas that you have just wiped off.</p>
